    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Nos <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/157">Paldolfus</persName> divina
                        ordinante providentia <rs key="#Princeps">Langobardorum gentis
                        princeps</rs>, <rs key="#Intercessory">per rogum</rs>
                        <persName key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus"><name ref="Garipertus"
                                >Gariperti</name>
                        </persName><rs key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">castaldei </rs><rs
                            key="#Personal_rank">dilecti</rs> nostri, concedimus in <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/84">Beati
                            Benedicti</orgName> confessoris Christi situs in <rs key="#Mountains"
                            >Monte</rs> Casino, ubi domnus <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/309"
                            >Aligernus</persName> venerabilis <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> preesse
                        videtur, <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Work_and_workers #Census #Datium #Servitium #Angaria"
                            >census et dationes seu angarias et omnem alium servitium</rs> que <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property">parti nostrae publice</rs> facere seu persolvere
                        debebit <persName key="#Work_and_workers #Census #Datium #Servitium #Angaria"
                                ><name ref="Lupelchis">Lupelchis</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">fili</rs> de <rs key="#Villages/settlements">Casa
                            Mesera</rs>, habitanti <rs key="#Vici">bico ubi dicitur Carpatelli</rs>,
                        non multum longe <rs key="#Churches">aecclesia Sancti Acapiti</rs>, vel
                        heredes eiusde. Ideo omne serbitium et dationem seu angarias que ipse
                        Lupelchisi vel heredes eius parti nostri publice facere semper solvere
                        debebit, totum sit in iam phato sancto monasterio concessum ad possessionem
                        iam dicti monasterii et de eiusque abbatibus vel rectoribus ad abendum et
                        faciendum exhinde que volueris, ita ut a nullis ex nostris comitibus,
                        castaldeis, iudicibus vel sculdahis habeant pars predicti monasterii de ea
                        omnia que superius legitur qualecumque molestiam aut contrarietatem, set
                        semper pars iam dicti monasterii et eiusque abbatibus et rectoribus habeant
                        et possideant ea omnia que superius legitur, et faciant exhinde omnia que
                        voluerint, nemine ibidem exhinde in aliquo contraria ingerente. Scripsi ego
                            <persName key="#Notary" ref="#people/337">Petrus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> ex iussione supradicte potestatis in anno
                        nono decimo principatus eius, mense Octuber, indictione quinta. Actum <rs
                            key="#Cities">civitate</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/173">Capuana</placeName>.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
